Egwuregwu
Ihe nkiri
Nke ka ewuewu
Ọnọdụ nchekwa ugbua riri ntuliaka mperi n'afọ a.

Dịka ndọrọndọrọọchịchị maka ntuliaka ọkwa Gọvanọ Anambra steeti si aga nke afọ 2021, ndị nọ n'isi ekwe mbipụta akụrụngwa e ji atụmgbere ntuliaka na-atule etu ndọrọndọrọọchịchị nke afọ 2017 si dị iche na nke 2021.
Na-agbanyeghi ya, obere ego batara nye ndị na-ebipụta ihe akụrụngwa ntuliaka afọ 2021.
Chiemela Mgbeahuru rụpụtara onyoonyo a.
Kirie ya n'uju:
NYSC Allowance: Gịnị ka ị ga-ejinwu N19,800 mee?
'Gọọmenti kwere nkwa inye m N5000 kwa ọnwa maka enweghị m onye olileanya mana ahụbeghị m tọrọ'
